-- Noir --

Noir gives Devilcat a curt nod, "Yes Sir." She saluts quietly, and 
then looks over at Torin.

"C'mon Torin, lets go." She leaves the control room, and heads for 
the cargo hold.


--- In nbwrpg@y..., "cardhead649" <cardhead649@y...> wrote:
> Riekan displays emotion for once: sadistic glee.  "So much for the 
> Forgotten Autobots," he sneers, watching the fireball of 
Vindicator's 
> demise slowly fade away.
> 
> "Now I can get back to my original train of thought," Devilcat 
says.  
> "Noir, you and Torin are going to dig out all the communicator 
beacons 
> you can find in the cargo hold.  I want them converted to jamming 
> stations.  Gatara, go check on the crash site; make sure our foes 
are 
> properly disposed of.  Riekan, keep working on the engine 
repairs.  If 
> any of you see Jayde, tell her I want to speak with her.  I'll be 
> keeping an eye on things here."
> 
> Gatara and Riekan move off to their assigned tasks ...
